{"tid":2189044,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內蒙古公安局將鼓動罷課　列作尋釁滋事","createTime":"2020-09-04T15:12:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T11:50:50.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"795c7cb9be8b83aa2cc36fad3ccc05ddc4d9dd76","tid":2189044,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T15:12:31.000Z","msg":"內蒙古部分中小學在開學日有家長和學生示威，反對當局逐步將教學語言統一為漢語。網上流傳片段，指有內蒙古政府人員上門，要求蒙古族家長不要參加遊行。<br />\n<br />\n巴彥淖爾市公安局亦發通告，指通過辱罵、恐嚇他人等方式，阻撓學生上課和鼓動學生罷課等行為，都會被視作尋釁滋事，屬於犯違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547928-20200904.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547928-20200904.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs4wKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=5e7775c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547928-20200904.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8f6fe05f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547928-20200904.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"d7ad0d6db0365df22020c5b02cbd6c2e1a7f6aef","tid":2189044,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T15:14:46.000Z","msg":"刁小學生親自指揮果然非一般咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee31ecaf29f3ca788375d2b2a4ef8f677f15c4d","tid":2189044,"uid":127929,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T15:20:23.000Z","msg":"好快會屈佢地蒙獨"},{"pid":"dc847d0e0343f8ce425df1d26e1c8fbcf4421c08","tid":2189044,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T15:21:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d5bc813d192b4a91c4c8a92dfa2d2d09e035308","tid":2189044,"uid":321255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T15:26:34.000Z","msg":"蒙古 加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b7bfa637b8be4830e8db939c810220ed8175ec","tid":2189044,"uid":62321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T17:11:32.000Z","msg":"極端核心恐怖主義苗頭"},{"pid":"984d859be0c71c257e7f8759d709e60e63d53922","tid":2189044,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T17:14:37.000Z","msg":"說是北宋的時候，常州有個叫田登的太守，對自己的名字特別忌諱，不允許其他人說「登」字，只要有人提到了這個字，必然惹得太守大怒，所以他身邊的吏卒很多不小心就被打板子了！<br />\n<br />\n於是整個常州都把「燈」字叫成火。而到了一年一度的元宵佳節。依照以往的慣例，州城裏都要放三天焰火，點三天花燈表示慶祝。而且州府衙門要提前貼出告示，讓老百姓到時候前來觀燈。<br />\n<br />\n可是這次，卻讓出告示的官員感到左右為難。怎麼寫呢？用上「燈」字，要觸犯太守；不用「燈」字，意思又表達不明白。<br />\n<br />\n想了好久，這個寫告示的官員告示上就寫成了「本州依例放火三日」。 告示貼出後，老百姓看了都驚吵喧鬧起來。尤其是一些外地來的客人，更是丈二和尚摸不着頭腦，還真的以為官府要在城裏放三天火呢！大家紛紛收拾行李，爭相離開這是非之地。當地的老百姓，平時對於田登的專制蠻橫無理已經是非常不滿，這次看了官府貼出的這張告示，更是氣憤萬分，忿忿地說：「只許州官放火，不許百姓點燈，這是什麼世道！"},{"pid":"ba34dd359cf6eff084e86facc2d6dde97b8b9eee","tid":2189044,"uid":254450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ee31ecaf29f3ca788375d2b2a4ef8f677f15c4d","tid":2189044,"uid":127929,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T15:20:23.000Z","msg":"好快會屈佢地蒙獨"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T17:25:49.000Z","msg":"蝗僞下次外訪果陣又要諗吓點答南蒙嘅人權問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0896a1028ae716185ea22381e77eca0f2576b8f","tid":2189044,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba34dd359cf6eff084e86facc2d6dde97b8b9eee","tid":2189044,"uid":254450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ee31ecaf29f3ca788375d2b2a4ef8f677f15c4d","tid":2189044,"uid":127929,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T15:20:23.000Z","msg":"好快會屈佢地蒙獨"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T17:25:49.000Z","msg":"蝗僞下次外訪果陣又要諗吓點答南蒙嘅人權問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T11:39:38.000Z","msg":"洗乜諗<br />\n<br />\n每次中共官員 被人問 新疆/西藏 問題<br />\n<br />\n佢地只有一個答案:「你想知, 可以自己親身去睇」"},{"pid":"206ae9629feaa879afe81df1ecde00411f51665e","tid":2189044,"uid":279357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T11:50:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jM8dCGIm6yc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjM8dCGIm6yc&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs4wKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=8edcc827\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jM8dCGIm6yc</a><br />\n蒙古🇲🇳加油💪反抗"}]}